      <JapaneseText>金髪でツンツン頭なんて
不良もいいとこだと思わねぇか、ヴェイグ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Blond, spiky hair...
Don't you think they've just gotta be hooligans, Veigue?</EnglishText>
